com.energyxxer.commodore.block

Class Block

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.block.Block

  • public class Block
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a block of a specific type, complete with blockstates and NBT data, which can be used with commands to place, fill, and test.
    See Also:
    Type, BlockType, Blockstate, TagCompound
